public static enum TSRPass.TSRAlgorithmType extends Enum<TSRPass.TSRAlgorithmType>
The TSRAlgorithmType enum represents the algorithm running mode to be used for super-resolution rendering in the TSRPass class.

Each enum value corresponds to a specific rendering mode, which affects the performance and quality of the super-resolution process.

Usage: TSRPass(TSRAlgorithmType)
